<div id="subtree-container" class="subtree-container"><div class="aea2d7dde423afa7ad9351a0886150a8-scss b51b00c1669ad99a1c607cd1e77c2824-scss" style="inset: 610px 269px 0px 0px; justify-content: flex-end;"><div class="afeebf1df237d4103108ba40799802d6-scss"><div class="c13443431e58facf06f9d12490b92a82-scss" style="width: 90vw; max-width: 8.5in;"><div class="_0df5ec6b9902d7d22ccfa3ebb4f35211-scss">Site Analysis</div><div class="e5e059a27f4c194020f0d961a3cb5989-scss" dir="auto"><div class="fr-view"><p><span class="fr-img-caption fr-fic fr-dii fr-fil fr-rounded fr-shadow" style="width: 150px;"><span class="fr-img-wrap"><img src="https://localweb-private.lodplanner.com/projects/4/plan-content/537ff971-dab1-4091-9955-01fda535c2f7-BIM%20Use%20Image%20-%20Site%20Analysis%202.jpg?Expires=1768831279&amp;Signature=mg8giuVH-qjYGWiHEQari-Sd55YlY9RfYw~L9EHZR7IDwPG2K1qIaed3lhklPeFfw-zVnVp29DsEAu9X0W9vTFjkLIks3uAnFD9lfLMSB4mniEceMtXEqU3Hp2VjrZEXGDeAyTfl803pTmk9Kj4CU99g4lzGOegfB6Fo7TyCWhOXLKRuU4RzpcRW42-rxkGbT4czpwiuBf4PtylBGyNn-~uGzyW-4XwpBuQIjIIwlHW42v0rtJ9Ow4vqfz2tdcmU5F3r3qvgxy4cpwruU08eeAEXTVK-FNICdg0UU2Kwr02RpZyCcJ8DsMxBQloeJSNiD2Gt34g25MN1dk2UhrnmPQ__&amp;Key-Pair-Id=APKAJRIVA6WNZT4BZJPQ" style="width: 150px;"><span class="fr-inner">Site Analysis</span></span></span>A process in which BIM/GIS tools are used to evaluate properties in a given area to determine the most optimal site location for a future project.&nbsp;</p>
<p>The site data collected is used to first select the site and then position the building based on other criteria.&nbsp;</p>
<p><br></p>
<table style="width: 100%;"><thead><tr><th><div style="text-align: left;">Potential Value:&nbsp;</div></th></tr></thead></table>
<ul>
<li>Use calculated decision making to determine if potential sites meet the required criteria according to project requirements, technical factors, and financial factors</li>
<li>Decrease costs of utility demand and demolition</li>
<li>Increase energy efficiency</li>
<li>Minimize risk of hazardous material</li>
<li>Maximize return on investment</li>
</ul>
<table style="width: 100%;"><thead><tr><th><div style="text-align: left;">Resources Required:</div></th></tr></thead></table>
<ul>
<li>GIS software</li>
<li>Design Authoring Software</li>
</ul>
<table style="width: 100%;"><thead><tr><th><div style="text-align: left;">Team Competencies Required:</div></th></tr></thead></table>
<ul>
<li>Ability to manipulate, navigate, and review a 3D model</li>
<li>Knowledge and understanding of local authorityâ€™s system (GIS, database information)</li>
</ul></div></div></div></div></div></div>